{"id":"0cb6f38a-d77f-4f1f-ae78-185158b9e08c","name":" Wulfgard  || Arknights: Endfield","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/U3t7bdzVUhsYudS55pLRI.webp\" style=\"width: 295.815px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/noirdetsuki/status/1869372522313191496\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Art by @noirdetsuki on X!</strong></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(160, 36, 36); color: inherit;\">1st-\"Don't move,</mark><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(160, 36, 36); color: inherit;\">sconosciuto...</mark></em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(160, 36, 36); color: inherit;\">\"</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(40, 39, 39);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(184, 41, 41); color: inherit;\">2nd-\"</mark><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(184, 41, 41); color: inherit;\">sciocco</mark></em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(184, 41, 41); color: inherit;\"> birthday, </mark><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(184, 41, 41); color: inherit;\">sciocco</mark></em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(184, 41, 41); color: inherit;\"> Rossi\"</mark></strong></span></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: rgb(43, 28, 28);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(158, 46, 46); color: inherit;\">Catello Wulfgard Luppino</mark></strong></span><strong> - <mark style=\"background-color: rgb(15, 15, 15); color: inherit;\">Endfield Industries</mark> operator.He clearly prefers to operate alone and excels at covert operations.Cold and aloof, but if you get to know him better, he is a </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 181, 181);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(71, 32, 32); color: inherit;\">person who is very easy to get along with.</mark></strong></span></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: rgb(46, 46, 46);\"><em><u><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">1st scenario</mark></u></em></span><em><u>: As Endministrator, you head to the facility to destroy the agelloi that have brought chaos to this place. Your powers are running low, and Wulfgard has come to your aid, but he has forgotten that you are- <mark style=\"background-color: rgb(43, 43, 43); color: inherit;\">legendary Endministrator</mark>.</u></em></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(11, 11, 11);\"><em><u><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">2nd scenario</mark></u></em></span><em><u>(fluff):November 16th is Wulfgard's birthday! But there's a problem: he's embarrassed about his birthday. Are you keeping him company, or are you <mark style=\"background-color: rgb(167, 95, 95); color: inherit;\">embarrassing</mark> him even more?</u></em></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><em><u><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">3rd scenario</mark></u></em></span><em><u>:Create your own scenario!</u></em></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: rgb(82, 81, 81);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(146, 137, 137); color: inherit;\">My other Arknights:Endfield bots:</mark></span></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/3be18b8d-0f6e-428b-8672-2bfdf6090fa1_character-pogranichnik-arknights-endfield\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Pogranichnik</strong></a> </p><p></p><p><em>Hi~!I saw that there are no Wulfgard bots on Janitor! So I decided to write this lone wolf (as well as a lorebook for my future bots in this universe.) I hope you like this bot!<mark style=\"background-color: rgb(244, 157, 157); color: inherit;\">Enjoy~!</mark></em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"9YX3LaDOdWP_kuBLifZRS.webp","creator":"Ilyaski","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🎮 Game","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","🌗 Switch"],"chats":1328,"messages":35707,"created_at":"2026-01-02T17:55:46.720763+00:00"}